components.name: AppDatepickerComponent

propertiesClass.name: rangeControl

components.templateData:
@if(range) {
<mat-form-field
  [class]="className"
  [appearance]="appearance"
  id="app-datepicker-range"
>
  <mat-label>{{ label }}</mat-label>

  <mat-date-range-input [formGroup]="rangeControl" [rangePicker]="pickerRange">
    <input
      matStartDate
      formControlName="start"
      [placeholder]="placeholderStart"
    />
    <input matEndDate formControlName="end" [placeholder]="placeholderEnd" />
  </mat-date-range-input>

  <mat-datepicker-toggle matIconSuffix [for]="pickerRange" />
  <mat-date-range-picker #pickerRange />
</mat-form-field>
} @else {
<mat-form-field
  id="app-datepicker"
  [class]="className"
  [formGroup]="group"
  [appearance]="appearance"
>
  <mat-label>{{ label }}</mat-label>

  <input
    matInput
    [id]="id"
    [name]="name"
    [matDatepicker]="picker"
    [placeholder]="placeholder"
    [formControlName]="formControlName"
  />
  <mat-datepicker-toggle matIconSuffix [for]="picker" />
  <mat-datepicker #picker />
</mat-form-field>
}

propertiesClass.name: form
propertiesClass.defaultValue: { radio: 1, select: 1, slider: 4, input: 'Teste', checkbox: true, fileUpload: [], imageCropper: null, textarea: 'Textarea', datepicker: new Date(), datepickerRange: { start: new Date(2023, 10, 10), end: new Date(2023, 10, 13), }, textEditor: `INITIAL`, sliderRange: { min: 2, max: 6 }, }

components.templateData:
<section id="form-example">
  <app-terminal-window [content]="form | json" />

  <form class="pt-8">
    <app-input
      name="input"
      label="Input"
      className="w-full"
      [(ngModel)]="form.input"
      [initialValue]="form.input"
    />

    <app-datepicker
      name="datepicker"
      label="Datepicker"
      className="w-full"
      [(ngModel)]="form.datepicker"
      [initialValue]="form.datepicker"
    />

    <app-datepicker
      range
      className="w-full"
      name="datepickerRange"
      label="Datepicker Range"
      [(ngModel)]="form.datepickerRange"
      [initialValue]="form.datepickerRange"
    />

    <app-select
      name="select"
      label="Select"
      className="w-full"
      [items]="defaultOptions"
      [(ngModel)]="form.select"
      [initialValue]="form.select"
    />

    <app-textarea
      name="textarea"
      label="Textarea"
      className="w-full"
      [(ngModel)]="form.textarea"
      [initialValue]="form.textarea"
    />

    <app-radio-button
      name="radio"
      label="Radio"
      [items]="defaultOptions"
      [(ngModel)]="form.radio"
      [initialValue]="form.radio"
    />

    <app-slider
      [min]="0"
      [max]="10"
      [step]="1"
      showTickMarks
      name="slider"
      label="Slider"
      [(ngModel)]="form.slider"
      [initialValue]="form.slider"
    />

    <app-slider
      range
      [min]="0"
      [max]="10"
      [step]="1"
      name="sliderRange"
      label="Slider Range"
      [(ngModel)]="form.sliderRange"
      [initialValue]="form.sliderRange"
    />

    <app-image-cropper
      name="imageCropper"
      [(ngModel)]="form.imageCropper"
      [initialValue]="form.imageCropper"
    />

    <app-file-upload
      [maxFiles]="5"
      name="fileUpload"
      label="File upload"
      [fileTypes]="['image/*']"
      placeholder="Insert fles"
      [(ngModel)]="form.fileUpload"
      [initialValue]="form.fileUpload"
    />

    <app-text-editor
      name="textEditor"
      className="w-full"
      label="Text editor"
      [(ngModel)]="form.textEditor"
      [initialValue]="form.textEditor"
    />

    <app-checkbox
      name="Checkbox"
      label="Checkbox"
      [(ngModel)]="form.checkbox"
      [initialValue]="form.checkbox"
    />

    <button class="btn-primary my-4" type="button" (click)="onSubmit()">
      Submit
    </button>
  </form>
</section>
